# Programmatic SEO pages

Low-volume, high-uniqueness pSEO. Every detail page must pass: unique body copy, real search intent, 2+ internal links.

## Routes (auto from content collections)

| Collection | URL | Layout |
|------------|-----|--------|
| `speaking/*.md` | `/speaking/{id}/` | `TalkLayout.astro` |
| `work/*.md` | `/work/{id}/` | `WorkLayout.astro` |
| `topics/*.md` | `/topics/{id}/` | `TopicLayout.astro` |

Slug = filename without extension (`kotlinconf-2024`, `n26`, `fraud-prevention`).

## Frontmatter cross-links

```yaml
relatedArticles: [article-id]
relatedTalks: [talk-id]
relatedWork: [work-id]        # speaking + topics only
```

Update **both directions** when linking (e.g. new talk → add to N26 work + fraud-prevention topic).

## Content quality gates

- **Talks:** body abstract required; verify `link` URL live
- **Work:** body narrative required; not résumé bullets alone
- **Topics:** 100+ word original intro in body; curated slugs only — no auto-tag pages

## Title/meta (set in `[...slug].astro` + layouts)

- Talk: `{title · event · Rafael Roman}` or `{event · Rafael Roman}`
- Work: `{role} at {company} · Rafael Roman}`
- Topic: `{title} · Topics · Rafael Roman}`

## Skip

Location doorway pages, glossary spam, tag archives < 3 articles.
